### FitAgent API 测试文件
### 在 VS Code 中安装 "REST Client" 扩展即可使用

@baseUrl = http://localhost:8000
@email = user@test.com
@password = password123

### 1. 登录获取 Token
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "{{email}}",
  "password": "{{password}}"
}

### 保存 token 到变量 (从上面响应中复制 token)
@token = YOUR_TOKEN_HERE

### 2. 设置 API Key
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/agent/config/api-key
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "api_key": "YOUR_DASHSCOPE_API_KEY"
}

### 3. 创建会话
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/agent/sessions
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "id": "1778234255682",
  "name": "测试会话"
}

### 4. 测试 /process 接口 (正确格式)
POST {{baseUrl}}/process
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "input": [
    {
      "content": [
        {
          "text": "帮我分析一下最近的饮食和训练情况",
          "type": "text"
        }
      ],
      "role": "user",
      "type": "message"
    }
  ],
  "session_id": "1778234255682"
}

### 5. 获取 API Key 状态
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/agent/config/api-key/status
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 6. 获取提示词模板
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/agent/config/prompts
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 7. 获取配置状态
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/agent/config/status
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
